  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We Are At Home Here II</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The objective of this project is to contribute to increased awareness and acceptance of elementary school students of the issue of migration and migrants living in Slovakia. Elementary school students&apos; experience with migration and migrants in Slovakia will be broadened and elementary school teachers will improve their ability to include neutral and objective information on migration and migrants in Slovakia in their curriculum. Three videos in the form of interviews with migrants will be produced to be used by elementary school teachers. Additionally, an educational manual will be updated and training of trainers will be organized.</narrative>
  </description>
